overview: A sequence of the drama series Kau, Aku, Kita. The story begins with a show of happiness or romance. Im Aus wakes Iman up in the morning with sweet words with 'abe' and 'sayang' between them and Iman started laughing because it was just an act. She still can't change the 'Kau' and 'Aku' calls between them.
title: Kau Aku Kita Raya
